snippet.title: Arcade Game: Guzzler (1983 Tehkan)
snippet.description:
A maze game where the player shoots 'liquid' to kill monsters. Eat 'food' to replace the liquid. Monsters are generated from 4 fires which must be destroyed to complete level.

Note: Used Invincibility cheat after down to last life. The Game is endless.
